uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.model.relationship

Interface RelationshipProvider<A extends AppUser,B extends DataObject>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - AppUser type
    B - Target type
    All Superinterfaces:
    AccessRoleProvider<A,B>, Contexed, Tagged
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRelationship, PersonRelationship, Relationship

    public interface RelationshipProvider<A extends AppUser,B extends DataObject>
extends AccessRoleProvider<A,B>, Tagged
    Interface for AccessRoleProvider classes that provide relationship roles between AppUsers and a target object where the set of provided relationships can be queried. These can be constructed dynamically.
